schema.description: This view joins data from the eket table with the calendar_date_dim table to provide a detailed view of Purchase Order Schedule lines, enriched with calendar dimensions for the Item Delivery Date and Order Date of the Schedule Line.  The data is at the granularity of individual schedule lines.
